title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 26 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 26 2022
description:
Uvalde aftermath: Questions are being asked as to why it took 90 minutes between the first 911 call and the gunman being shot dead. Distressing videos show parents begging cops to stop Texas school shooting. Beto O'Rourke calls Governor Abbott “Evil". C&B take calls from law enforcement officers to weigh in on Uvalde shooting.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
